wikipedia_page.main: Edward "Peter" Mooney (born 22 March 1897) was an English professional footballer who played as a right half.

response: Peter Mooney (born August 19, 1983) is a Canadian actor, known for his role as Officer Nick Collins on the police drama series Rookie Blue and for playing Sir Kay on the historical fantasy series Camelot.
Peter Mooney married Canadian actress Sarah Power in July 2017.
